<div class="content-container">
<div class="post-intro"></div><div class="storytelling-sections"><h2 class="section-heading">The Venue:<br/>this's Romantic Charm</h2><div class="featured-image"><img alt="Geeta + Vir - The Venue" class="section-image" loading="lazy" src="https://acromatico.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Indian-Wedding-NY-001-1024x683.jpg"/><p class="image-caption">Geeta + Vir - The Venue moment 1</p></div><h2 class="section-heading">The Ceremony:<br/>A Heartfelt Intimate Exchange</h2><div class="featured-image"><img alt="Geeta + Vir - The Ceremony" class="section-image" loading="lazy" src="https://acromatico.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Indian-Wedding-NY-032.jpg"/><p class="image-caption">Geeta + Vir - The Ceremony moment 2</p></div><h2 class="section-heading">Couple Portraits:<br/>Geeta's Natural Chemistry</h2><div class="featured-image"><img alt="Geeta + Vir - Couple Portraits" class="section-image" loading="lazy" src="https://acromatico.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Indian-Wedding-NY-064-1024x682.jpg"/><p class="image-caption">Geeta + Vir - Couple Portraits moment 3</p></div><h2 class="section-heading">The Reception:<br/>Stunning Celebration &amp; Joyful Moments</h2><div class="featured-image"><img alt="Geeta + Vir - The Reception" class="section-image" loading="lazy" src="https://acromatico.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Indian-Wedding-NY-094.jpg"/><p class="image-caption">Geeta + Vir - The Reception moment 4</p></div><h2 class="section-heading">Photography Approach:<br/>Authentic Moments in Natural Light</h2><div class="featured-image"><img alt="Geeta + Vir - Photography Approach" class="section-image" loading="lazy" src="https://acromatico.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Indian-Wedding-NY-127-1024x683.jpg"/><p class="image-caption">Geeta + Vir - Photography Approach moment 5</p></div></div>
